  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Medico-economics assessment (cost-effectiveness) of the unilateral carotid barostimulation
      with Barostim NeoTM compared to usual care in patients with resistant hypertension
      (multicenter randomized, PROBE trial), followed-up for 12 months, with a lifetime-long
      modeling.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
